    <item>
      <title>Pregnancy Wellness</title>
      <link>https://birthwithiraivi.com/courses/pregnancy-wellness/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>https://birthwithiraivi.com/courses/pregnancy-wellness/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Nurture your body, mind, and baby throughout pregnancy with practical guidance on healthy living, nutrition, movement, relaxation, and emotional well-being. This session helps you stay active, build a deeper connection with your baby, and prepare both physically and mentally for a positive birth experience.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;topics-included&#34;&gt;Topics Included:&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pregnancy nutrition&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Healthy lifestyle habits&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pregnancy-safe exercises&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pelvic preparation&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Breathing techniques&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Relaxation &amp;amp; mindfulness&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Prenatal bonding&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Visualization techniques&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Partner bonding activities&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Preparing body and mind for birth&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pelvic preparation and mobility&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Optimal fetal positioning&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Birth-focused movement&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Relaxation and breathing techniques&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Building confidence for labor&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Birth affirmations and visualization&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Partner support strategies&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Creating a positive birth mindset&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
