    <item>
      <title>Preparing for Birth</title>
      <link>https://birthwithiraivi.com/courses/preparing-for-birth/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>https://birthwithiraivi.com/courses/preparing-for-birth/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Feel confident and prepared for your baby&amp;rsquo;s birth with practical guidance on labor, birth, and comfort techniques. Learn what to expect during labor, understand your options, and discover ways to manage the process with greater calm and confidence. With the right knowledge and support, you can approach childbirth as a positive and empowering experience.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;topics-included&#34;&gt;Topics Included:&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Understanding Birth Physiology&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Recognising the Signs of Labor&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Stages of Labor &amp;amp; Birth&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Comfort Measures &amp;amp; Pain Management Options&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Relaxation &amp;amp; Visualisation Techniques&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Induction and Medical Interventions&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Labor &amp;amp; Birth Positions&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Creating Your Birth Preferences Plan&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;The Golden Hour After Birth&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Delayed Cord Clamping&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Understanding the Apgar Score&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;The Role of the Birth Partner&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Postpartum Recovery &amp;amp; Healing Tips&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Breastfeeding Preparation</title>
      <link>https://birthwithiraivi.com/courses/breastfeeding-preparation/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>https://birthwithiraivi.com/courses/breastfeeding-preparation/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Prepare for a successful breastfeeding journey with practical guidance on latching, milk production, and newborn feeding patterns. Learn what to expect during the early weeks of life and how to support a healthy milk supply for your baby.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;topics-included&#34;&gt;Topics Included:&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;The Golden Hour After Birth&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Understanding Breastfeeding Basics&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Latching Positions &amp;amp; Techniques&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Understanding Milk Production&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Supporting a Healthy Milk Supply&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Baby&amp;rsquo;s Feeding Cues &amp;amp; Feeding Patterns&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Milk Expression, Pumping &amp;amp; Storage&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Common Breastfeeding Challenges &amp;amp; Solutions&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Breastfeeding Myths &amp;amp; Facts&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Breastfeeding in the Early Weeks&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Returning to Work &amp;amp; Breastfeeding&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Gentle Weaning and Transitioning&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Fourth Trimester Care</title>
      <link>https://birthwithiraivi.com/courses/fourth-trimester-care/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>https://birthwithiraivi.com/courses/fourth-trimester-care/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Prepare for a confident transition into parenthood with guidance on postpartum recovery and newborn care. Learn what to expect after birth, how to support your physical and emotional wellbeing, and gain practical knowledge to care for your baby during the early weeks of life. This session helps you feel informed, supported, and ready for the fourth trimester.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;topics-included&#34;&gt;Topics Included:&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Maternal Recovery After Birth&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Postpartum Warning Signs&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Baby Blues &amp;amp; Postpartum Mood Changes&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Self-Care for New Mothers&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Understanding Your Newborn&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Newborn Care &amp;amp; Comfort Measures&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Newborn Health Checks &amp;amp; Screenings&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Diapering, Bathing &amp;amp; Umbilical Cord Care&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Infant Massage Basics&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Newborn Feeding &amp;amp; Growth Expectations&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Safe Sleep Guidelines&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;When to Seek Medical Attention&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Common Postpartum &amp;amp; Newborn Care Myths&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
